  documentBody: 'Kamalassi:


    I regretfully inform you that considering my personal
    circumstances, I am unable to continue my work as a PDM at SuckLard Inc.


    I
    want to express my heartfelt thanks for your mentorship over the past two years,
    and I regret the necessity of this decision. I appreciate your understanding.
    If there is anything I can do to help during the transition, please let me know.

'
